e beigefügt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Sep 2021) 0aArchitecturexPhilosophy. 0aArchitecture. 4aAldo Rossi. 4aArchitekturtheorie. 7aARCHITECTURE / Criticism.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1z978311075070608iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2019z978311071956708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Architecture and Design 2019z9783110605747oZDB-23-DAD08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG0 cEPUBz97830382168340 cprintz978303821516540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978303821221840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783038212218423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783038212218/original  a978-3-11-071956-7  DG Plus eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-075070-6  DG Plus DeG Package 2021 Part 1b2021  aEBA_CL_AD  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DADb2019  aZDB-23-DGGb2019